        "alt_text": "NASA\\u2019s 2026 Earth Day poster. It shows Earthset captured through the Orion spacecraft window during the Artemis II crew\\u2019s flyby of the Moon. A muted blue Earth with bright white clouds sets behind the cratered lunar surface. The dark portion of Earth is experiencing nighttime. On Earth\\u2019s day side, swirling clouds are visible over the Australia and Oceania region. The Moon is in the foreground of the image. A quote from astronaut Victor Glover is displayed just above Earth. It reads: \\u201CIn all of this emptiness\\u2026 you have this oasis, this beautiful place that we get to exist together.\\u201D Along the bottom of the poster are the words \\u201CEarth Day\\u201D and \\u201CThe Journey Starts Here.\\u201D The NASA and Artemis logos are in the top right corner.",
        "height": 960,
        "media_key": "3_2047016022427729920",
        "public_metrics": {},
        "type": "photo",
        "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGh2OhJWgAAMYYR.jpg",
